    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Welcome to my Data Science Portfolio\"\ndescription: \"Data analysis, machine learning and visualization expert\"\nlang: en\nformat:\n  html:\n    page-layout: custom\n    toc: false\n---\n\n::: hero-banner\n# Transform your data into strategic decisions\n\n## And move faster than your competitors.\n\nSpecialized in data analysis, machine learning and interactive visualization, I can help you with your data science projects from A to Z.\n\n[Discover my services](/services/){.btn .btn-primary .btn-lg} [View my portfolio](/portfolio/){.btn .btn-outline-secondary .btn-lg}\n:::\n\n## My Expertise\n\n:::::: grid\n::: g-col-md-4\n### 📊 Data Analysis\n\nExploration, cleansing and statistical analysis of your data to reveal hidden patterns and generate actionable insights.\n:::\n\n::: g-col-md-4\n### 🤖 Machine Learning\n\nDevelopment of predictive models and machine learning algorithms tailored to your business needs.\n:::\n\n::: g-col-md-4\n### 📈 Visualization\n\nCreate interactive dashboards and engaging visualizations to effectively communicate your results.\n:::\n::::::\n\n## Recent Projects\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"plotly html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-69f90f9228d5f78bec22\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-69f90f9228d5f78bec22\">{\"x\":{\"visdat\":{\"2079311492b1\":[\"function () \",\"plotlyVisDat\"]},\"cur_data\":\"2079311492b1\",\"attrs\":{\"2079311492b1\":{\"x\":{},\"y\":{},\"text\":{},\"hovertemplate\":\"<b>%{text}<\\/b><br>Complexité: %{x}<br>Impact: %{y}%<br>Durée: %{marker.size} semaines<br><extra><\\/extra>\",\"color\":{},\"size\":{},\"alpha_stroke\":1,\"sizes\":[10,100],\"spans\":[1,20],\"type\":\"scatter\",\"mode\":\"markers\",\"inherit\":true}},\"layout\":{\"margin\":{\"b\":40,\"l\":60,\"t\":25,\"r\":10},\"title\":\"Vue d'ensemble de mes projets récents\",\"xaxis\":{\"domain\":[0,1],\"automargin\":tru